{"tid":1830923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟公共場所 擬禁用人臉識別","createTime":"2020-01-20T04:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T04:34:29.000Z","uid":144626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abb51d87d5e5838ff22854306ba52d634fe1d15d","tid":1830923,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"人臉識別技術爭議不斷，英國警方日前於威爾斯卡迪夫球場外，試用人臉識別技術掃描球迷，並拘捕曾被列入黑名單的人，引起大量球迷不滿。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道指，歐盟委員會擬在3至5年內，禁止在公共場所使用人臉識別技術，以便研究如何防止相關技術被濫用。<br />\n<br />\n3至5年內實施 研措施防濫用<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報道，歐盟委員會在一份長達18頁的白皮書中提出，計劃在3至5年內，禁止所有人在公共場所使用人臉識別技術。委員會指出，必須盡快更新監管政策，包括有時間限制地禁止使用人臉識別技術，加強保護大眾私隱及數據。白皮書亦寫到，在禁令期間，可以評估人臉識別技術帶來的影響，以及制定風險管理措施。<br />\n<br />\n文件亦建議人工智能（AI）的開發者和用戶均要承擔責任，新政策實施後，歐盟國家亦應該任命相關機構進行監督。歐盟委員會將在最終決定前徵求反饋意見，而歐盟競爭事務專員韋斯塔格（Margrethe Vestager）將於下月提出建議。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：黃懌勤"},{"pid":"8b1bee665ec7fb80aa16928c8c24cb3a03615244","tid":1830923,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"合理，歐洲人一向重視私隱<br />\n不過德國個總理奶到雪雪聲"},{"pid":"06d5e6996be3b45485cd5061177a8f7ba837094c","tid":1830923,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=1ff4640c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n而家美帝要求強国簽左第二階段先撤關稅<br />\n所以強国一定要被迫情況下同美帝簽協議<br />\n香港要搭順風車<br />\n<br />\n另外, 所羅門聯署:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=cef55731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again</a>"},{"pid":"eb3d750207458f1dad769df227a6270f09a14e88","tid":1830923,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1bee665ec7fb80aa16928c8c24cb3a03615244","tid":1830923,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"合理，歐洲人一向重視私隱<br />\n不過德國個總理奶到雪雪聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:17:23.000Z","msg":"合理，歐洲人一向只係重視歐洲人"},{"pid":"8120d295910f57124f1919fdc97ccc34ea3f017e","tid":1830923,"uid":287206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1bee665ec7fb80aa16928c8c24cb3a03615244","tid":1830923,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"合理，歐洲人一向重視私隱<br />\n不過德國個總理奶到雪雪聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"歐洲人重視私隱就唔會用屎為用得咁開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cc389d86dc19a3cdb435275175ba97f72f72d2","tid":1830923,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1bee665ec7fb80aa16928c8c24cb3a03615244","tid":1830923,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"合理，歐洲人一向重視私隱<br />\n不過德國個總理奶到雪雪聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"個死八婆幾時先肯落台"},{"pid":"dff2b96560d24dadaf3d59b18c1158eaf458bac1","tid":1830923,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8120d295910f